      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CINNAMON (1) had a tough draw last start and worked in the previous outing so prepared to forgive those results. Had been racing well with a string of top-three finishes prior including back-to-back Narrabri wins. The ace draw gives her every chance to show her best. MCCRIKEY NZ (8) impressed when returning to winning form in good style last start. Draws on the back row but is building a good record at this circuit and distance. TINNY MAHONEY (9) made a nice return at his latest appearance here a week ago, coming from this row for third. Fitter and this is a nice drop in class so he can build on that bright start to the campaign. THE TAX CULLECTOR (3) has been coming from the back row but won at this venue the last time he started on the front line so can produce his best today.",
